text: Ibrahim Mohamed Solih (އިބްރާހީމް މުޙައްމަދު ޞާލިޙް; born 1 March 1962), better known as Ibu (އިބޫ), is a Maldivian politician. He was the President of the Maldives from 17 November 2018 until 17 November 2023. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the Maldives Category:1962 births Category:Current national leaders
title: Ibrahim Mohamed Solih
